subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened national capacities for implementation of HIV funds and programmes, including those financed through multilateral initiatives like the Global Fund to fight AIDS, Tuberculosis, and Malaria
subproject.description: The overall goal of the strategic plan of the national tuberculosis program is to reduce the burden of tuberculosis in Angola. This is to be accomplished by strengthening the provision of DOTS through the country with an emphasis on eleven provinces where most of Angola reside.
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
